  "title": "Dental Surgery Assistant",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Prepare dental operatories for patient arrival ensure all instruments, materials and equipment are ready</li>\n  <li>Attend to all patients seeking treatments and/or making inquiries at the clinic promptly and courteously.</li>\n  <li>Maintain and ensure the cleanliness of the clinic and treatment room.</li>\n  <li>Maintain dental equipment and instruments in good working condition.</li>\n  <li>Discharge patients by dispensing medication, collecting payment, and scheduling of next appointment.</li>\n  <li>Develop X-ray/OPG for assessment of treatment.</li>\n  <li>No prior experience is required; training will be provided.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
